ed the researcher to brag about it.\n\n10 partners including apple, google, microsoft, and nvidia are now using it to secure critical software. $100M in credits. confirmed it wont be released to the public.\n\nAI is now better than most humans at breaking software. defenders need to move fast.\n\nhttps://www.anthropic.com/glasswing\n\n#ai #security #anthropic", "photos": [], "videos": []}, {"id": "57", "text": "https://fixupx.com/hrithikk/status/2041800069041811950?s=20", "photos": ["https://cdn4.telesco.pe/file/la0_Ay7lkX5MIALEK4XezfVZq6FC5OKoHKbyZLk61srp6nTUbB5MePRRo0GGq_O6KF7S1W9WSp32GvljXZPP2Zq4nooKx9c_Cs8M9J4PYLU4YQ3kGv-VRvE8vejxKIzVkQJrxydxzx6nELhQEWzOH2RPgxMZiW-MW2YiW25Y1nKAOQp7LMXdzxsD-9AfkhbejrWsXB6QLr-hEhQuD1pUOsXkOKmhRQGGOX9BhKQDZ6_afqHbWdUiQOgTnW_AUsoGiyhDk8YHW917AXk1_Be7G0PnENlMyZbaoMOBinbDmid-JMXDjZyiPN-evTLamJdtJsHhc6n7SvTh0qP6NKi72w.jpg"], "videos": []}, {"id": "49", "text": "SOMEONE MADE A DIGITAL WHIP TO MAKE CLAUDE WORK FASTER 💀\n\nhttps://x.com/yaml/status/2041108141266653325", "photos": ["https://cdn4.telesco.pe/file/C4ZgWyB0srpyZqsS1GNG0As4rD8dpx2Bdd__Ng69BnLtHRltrGW1pn7lYkgkOX77G0RaTfxjXsxPqKhvXi4fa-4slG7XYnkPWKr7vQUho4s8xMZAKQ-AuwxampPAC6Oie3hzxk_gCHzRjjaNlIiDaqDde2e7cljZ-RsbS1m-IR6VMGZoiMUHRvENUO6hYLKpvWbcNQdnDc5jQmoqE7fnB-kbnyU0DpnQ-t3YLrcnG28xaGu2sRtlS28YlBoB65a3g1luIdm3TGQwbzsURGomA29YaqpFUDDMGLifH4GXWzBh8Y6GwLApIAXReSONeUTuSXZhhTqyhVJw5yiIGAHU_w"], "videos": ["videos/49.mp4"]}, {"id": "48", "text": "fieldtheory cli syncs all your X bookmarks locally so your AI agent can actually read and search them. free, open source by andrewfarah\n\nfieldtheory.dev/cli\ngithub.com/afar1/fieldtheory-cli\nnpm install -g fieldtheory\n\n#ai #webdev #tool", "photos": ["https://cdn4.telesco.pe/file/K2IS6tiTOwgjRTDDUSE2WnY5ka8AFR4KT_HRdmBMlbBCPr7BEGnaKqHQ8gcbUPUPXYcvCyaBHA_Ko9GJwUZDorPqHOJdA6Z-Eb2oix0bU-OY_9Gjlqo211yT__PhWgO_1nBy8IAu7C5fsnUaytCMds9KjOnKMXCPDbcrSjUlfGUGltnqmEKGCvDUWQ4rT6lIO-BIoH0UBzqfZr9bMMOC-FnctYUcmXiUYt0QctV-6MknmhOXT8KDfTdq0rCdpdtq2W7CbGL